=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據84條點評持有35%的新鮮度，平均得分4.7／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/project_almanac/ |title=Project Almanac |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2015-02-07 |archive-date=2015-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209064514/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/project_almanac/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；該網站共識：「《跨界失控》不是沒有智慧和創意，但其輕薄的故事和刺激性發展，鏡頭的攝影最終使其很難讓人推薦」。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於25位評論家得分47（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/project-almanac |title=Project Almanac Reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |date= |accessdate=2015-02-04 |archive-date=2015-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207064357/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/project-almanac |dead-url=no }}</ref>，口碑普通。

